![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/27e68849-7533-40c3-93b1-32683299a549/ep331.jpg)

We're capping off our 3-part Anime series with the most recent mainstream adaptation: Batman Ninja. In Batman Ninja, the Dark Knight and his enemies are transported from modern-day Gotham City to feudal Japan by Gorilla Grodd’s time displacement machine. The film follows Batman’s struggle to adapt to this new era while facing off against familiar foes in a unique setting The movie combines stunning anime visuals with the iconic Batman universe, but does the mixture work for contemporary fans? You'll have to tune in to find out!  
  
Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  

